          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "In this case, the Ferrari F40 Gold had found was stolen. He didn’t know that at first, but since it was such a big purchase, the guy flew out to Japan to inspect the supercar in person. Asking about the serial number, he quickly found out it had been stolen in Italy back in 1996.",
